description: TEHRAN – Iranian President Masoud Pezeshkian who started a three-day tour of Iraq on Wednesday arrived in Erbil, the capital of Iraq’s Kurdistan Region, on Thursday, where he was officially welcomed by Nechirvan Barzani, the president of the Kurdistan Region.
title: Pezeshkian makes milestone visit to Iraqi Kurdistan Region

description: TEHRAN - The Iranian Foreign Ministry on Thursday separately summoned the heads of the British, French, German and Dutch embassies following accusations that Iran had delivered missiles to Russia and imposed new sanctions against the Islamic Republic.
title: Iran summons four European diplomats over claims of missile delivery to Russia

description: TEHRAN – Russian President Vladimir Putin held talks on Thursday with Iran’s Supreme National Security Council secretary Ali Akbar Ahmadian in St. Petersburg, the venue of the meeting of BRICS’s top security officials.
title: Putin meets Iran’s security chief in St. Petersburg

description: TEHRAN- Seyyed Ammar Hakim, who hosted Pezeshkian and his accompanying delegation in the presence of Prime Minister al-Sudani, appreciated the message of the Supreme Leader of the Islamic Revolution Ayatollah Seyyed Ali Khamenei to the people of Iraq for successfully hosting the Arbaeen processions.
title: Hakim appreciates Iran's leader message to Iraq
